ADDITIONAL NOTE ON ORACLE BINARIES AND DOCUMENTATION

This repository contains educational scripts (.sh / .ps1 / .sql) that interact
with Oracle Database, Oracle Linux, and VirtualBox. These scripts do NOT
include any Oracle proprietary binaries, response files specific to a given
license, or copyrighted Oracle documentation excerpts.

Standard RMAN operations such as BACKUP DATABASE, RESTORE, DUPLICATE, and the
RMAN catalog itself do NOT require additional Oracle licenses beyond Oracle
Database SE2 / EE.

Diagnostic Pack and Tuning Pack are NOT used by this subproject. AWR/ASH
queries (which require Diagnostic Pack) are NOT included here.

The user is responsible for compliance with their Oracle license terms when
running these scripts against Oracle products.
